From f50a6828e276d0223757f4d5fd237d5ba684db9e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: JoaoMateus66 <ra867618@ucdb.br>
Date: Thu, 12 Mar 2026 18:08:37 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] perf(frontend): heavy optimization pass for weak
 mobile/desktop devices

- Auto-scroll reduced from 30fps to 20fps (50ms interval, 5px/tick)
- Skip perspective calculations on mobile in both carousels
- Replace UpscalableHeroImage with ProxiedImage (removes POST /api/images/upscale, saves RAM + network)
- Merge 3 stacked DecoratedBox gradients into single CustomPaint in FeaturedOverlay
- ShimmerBox: AnimatedBuilder+Container  CustomPainter (avoids new BoxDecoration/LinearGradient objects per frame)
- MiniPosterCard hover scale reduced from 1.45x to 1.25x
- Replace AnimatedContainer+Clip.antiAlias with ClipRRect+Clip.hardEdge in PosterCard/MiniPosterCard
- Replace AnimatedContainer with DecoratedBox+SizedBox in NavArrowButton and CarouselArrow
- Remove boxShadow from play icons in carousels (expensive GPU blur)
- Reduce boxShadow in AnimeCardHover (blur 106, remove when not hovered)
- TranslatableText: AnimatedSwitcher 300ms150ms, replace shimmer gradient overlay with tiny spinner
- FadeTransition(AlwaysStoppedAnimation) replaces AnimatedOpacity in section_row perspective
- addAutomaticKeepAlives: false in MyListPage SliverGrid
